Algorithm, provider, and capability listing

Usage: openssl list [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --digest-commands     List available message digest algorithms
      --cipher-commands     List available symmetric cipher algorithms
      --mac-algorithms      List available MAC algorithms
      --kdf-algorithms      List available KDF algorithms
      --public-key-methods  List available public key methods
      --disabled            List features disabled in this build
      --providers           List loaded providers
      --all-algorithms      List all available algorithms across all categories
  -h, --help                Print help
